Package: vkR
Type: Package
Title: Access to VK API via R
Description: Provides an interface to the VK API <https://vk.com/dev/methods>.
      VK <https://vk.com/> is the largest European online social networking
      service, based in Russia.
Version: 0.1
Date: 2016-12-01
